<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Bloccit</h1>
  <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
  <p>
    <% if !current_user %>
      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> or 
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-large' %> today!
      <% end %>
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Make the Internet's Front Page news!</h2>
    <p>Post the best links that you find on the Internet and share them. If your links are particularly awesome, you will rise to the top!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Quickly find the Best of the Best!</h2>
    <p>Quickly get your eyes on some of the best and most interesting information found on the Internet!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4">
    <h2>Join our Community of Information Explorers!</h2>
    <p>Join forces with other explorers out looking around and finding interesting things online.</p>
  </div>
</div>

